name: organic essential oils  - Week Box
description:
Relieve daily stress & minor injuries with organic essential oils from France by Solyvia.

WeekBox contains three different 5ml essential oils for the body.

1. BugSafe - A combination of Macadamia nut oil and macerated St. Johns Wort with essential oils of: Lavender, Citronella Java, Stageriana Eucalyptus, Pelargonium Graveolens, Tea Tree, Laricio Pine and Dwarf Juniper.

The anti-insect soothing shield: no more insects will  bug  you again ! A roll-on to always have at hand for an outdoor weekend trip with kids. Thanks to the synergy of organic vegetable oils and organic essential oils, it helps to relieve pain of insect bites (mosquitoes, wasps, spiders ...) while keeping them away, and it also reduces redness, itching and the feelings of irritation.

2. Head'Ake - Head'Ake - A combination of Macadamia nut oil and Borage with essential oils of: True Lavender, Chamomile, Basil, Laurus Nobilis, Peppermint, Clove and Wintergreen.

The synergy of essential oils of this roll-on soothes and calms the feeling of heavy head, as well as the tensions in the neck and shoulders, it is also very useful for traveling in prevention of motion sickness (plane, car, boat...)

3. Cut'n'Bump - A combination of Nigella, Calophylle, macerated St. Johns Wort, Arnica and Calendula, with essential oils of: Helichrysum, Wild Carrot, Dwarf Juniper, Rockrose, True Lavender and Tea Tree

The bulwark against wounds Designed for the whole family, this roll-on is essential for all the little worries of everyday life: bumps, bruises, minor burns... It helps to relieve pain, promotes sanitation and scarring of the skin if needed and prevents the formation of hematoma in cases of shock

We offer free shipping within Australia.
